
BUILDING
• building materials (up to you)
• flourescent light fixture
• PVC pipe
• flexible tubing
• vase
• plants

WIRING
• soldering iron & solder
• regular wire & jumper wires
• heat shrink (or some way to secure wires)

COMPONENTS
• arduino uno
• low voltage pump
• RGB LEDs
• 4 buttons
• resistors for the buttons/LEDs
• 2 relays 
• switch (120v)
• realtime clock: https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00LZCTMJM/ref=oh_aui_detailpage_o03_s00?ie=UTF8&psc=1
• LCD screen: https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B01GPUMP9C/ref=oh_aui_detailpage_o09_s01?ie=UTF8&psc=1

just a note, the code relies on using that specific clock and that specific LCD screen.
